Handler

Class TileImageHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • Handler.TileImageHandler

  • public class TileImageHandler
extends java.lang.Object
    This class will read all the tileimages in a specific directory. The reading of the file is done in the class constructor. After this is done, other classes may use this class to retrieve images of tiles, by supplying the tile id.
    Version:
    2013-02-11
    Author:
    Johan
